- set_meta_tags title: '点字グループトーク'
- set_meta_tags description: 'コメント通知が一覧で表示されます。'

.section-title 通知一覧

- if @notifications.size == 0
  .flex.flex-col.items-center.my-4
    p.text-sm.text-gray-500 通知はありません
    = lucide_icon('package-open', class: 'stroke-gray-500 w-10 h-10 inline-block m-4')
- else
  .m-4.text-center.space-y-2
    - @notifications.each do |notification|
      = render 'notification', notification: notification
    = paginate @notifications
  
  - if @notifications.any?(read: false)
    = button_to '全て既読にする', allmarks_path, class: 'text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 active:text-blue-900 underline transition'

.m-4
  = link_to dashboard_path, class: 'flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 active:text-blue-900 transition' do
    = lucide_icon("chevron-left").html_safe
    | ダッシュボードへ戻る
